  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , my master , I , Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , the child born to Ninagala , chosen by Nanše in the heart , given strength by Ninĝirsu , called by a propitious name by Bau , given wisdom by Enki , who submits to the orders of Inana , the beloved slave of Lugal-Uruba , the beloved of Dumuzid-abzu , dug a pit ... kuš ( deep ) . I sifted its earth as if ( I were searching for ) gems , carried around fire as if it were ( to be made ritually ) pure . I had ( the temple ) stand wide like a bull . I returned the earth into ( the pit ) , constructed its ... foundation pit . On it I built a 10 kuš ( high ) substructure , ( and ) on the substructure I built E-ninnu-anzud-babbar 30 kuš ( high ) for ( Ninĝirsu )"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.28",
      "line_range": "28",
      "translation": "(iii 8) For Ninḫursaĝa , the mother of all children , I built her temple in Ĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.31",
      "line_range": "31",
      "translation": "(iv 3) For Bau , the kind woman , the child of An , I built her temple in Iri-kug ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.36",
      "line_range": "36",
      "translation": "(iv 8) For Inana , the lady of Kugnuna , I built her temple in Urub ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.39",
      "line_range": "39",
      "translation": "(iv 11) For Enki , king of Eridug , I built his temple in Ĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.42",
      "line_range": "42",
      "translation": "(v 2) For Nindara , the mighty master , I built his temple ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.43",
      "line_range": "43",
      "translation": "(v 3) For Ninagala , my 1 personal god , I built his temple ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.48",
      "line_range": "48",
      "translation": "(v 8) For Ninmarki , the kind woman , the firstborn child of Nanše , I built the Ešgutur , the temple chosen in her heart ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.53",
      "line_range": "53",
      "translation": "(vi 1) For En-sig-nun , Ningirsu's donkey herdsman , I built his E-dura ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.57",
      "line_range": "57",
      "translation": "(vi 5) For Ĝeštin-ana , lady of those who gathered ( in the netherworld ) , I built her temple in Ĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001466.61",
      "line_range": "61",
      "translation": "(vi 9) For Dumuzid-abzu , lady of Kinunir , I built her temple in Ĝirsu ."
    }
  ],
